## 7.6 Email Notification System

### 7.6.1 SMTP Configuration

```typescript
interface SMTPConfig {
  host: string;
  port: number;
  secure: boolean;
  auth: {
    user: string;
    pass: string;  // From secrets manager
  };
  from: {
    name: string;  // 'MMS Notifications'
    address: string;  // 'mms-noreply@metro.example'
  };
}
```

### 7.6.2 Notification Types

| Type | Trigger | Recipients | Template |
|------|---------|------------|----------|
| `DRIFT_ALERT` | Drift threshold exceeded | Planners | drift_alert.html |
| `OVERLOAD_WARNING` | Week utilization >100% | Depot managers | overload_warning.html |
| `PM_REMINDER` | PM due in 7 days | Depot managers | pm_reminder.html |
| `BASELINE_PUBLISHED` | New baseline published | All planners | baseline_published.html |
| `OPTIMIZER_FAILED` | Optimizer job failed | System admins | optimizer_failed.html |
| `FILE_MISSING` | No mileage file received | Data team | file_missing.html |
| `MATERIAL_SHORTAGE` | Blocking parts unavailable | Procurement | material_shortage.html |

